{
  "_comment": [
    "David's home Record mount tree.",
    "",
    "Pubkeys marked TODO need to be derived and filled in before use.",
    "For 'ours:true' entries: derive via `signer.keysFor(mountName)` from",
    "David's credentials (username/password from env/secrets/david.env).",
    "For 'ours:false' entries: fill in the foreign Record's pubkey once",
    "the corresponding Record is authored (Turnstone Record, wake-watcher",
    "Record).",
    "",
    "Small helper to derive an 'ours' pubkey (run once, paste result here):",
    "  set -a; source env/secrets/david.env; set +a",
    "  node -e \"const {Signer}=await import('./public/streamo/Signer.js'); \\",
    "           const {bytesToHex}=await import('./public/streamo/utils.js'); \\",
    "           const s=new Signer(process.env.STREAMO_USERNAME, \\",
    "                              process.env.STREAMO_PASSWORD, \\",
    "                              +process.env.STREAMO_KEY_ITERATIONS); \\",
    "           const k=await s.keysFor('wake-inbox'); \\",
    "           console.log(bytesToHex(k.publicKey))\""
  ],
  "mounts": {
    "wake-inbox/": {
